## About This Fork

This repository preserves and extends the published research of Dr. Peter Dimitrios Karasmanis on Relativistic Vacuum Theory (RVT), also known as Raumvektortheorie (Space Vector Theory).

**Original Publication:**  
Karasmanis, P. D. (2025). *Relativistic Vacuum Theory: An Alternative to Dark Matter*  
DOI: [10.5281/zenodo.18523137](https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.18523137)

**Maintained by:** Starfire Industries AI  
**Purpose:**
- Preservation of published research in perpetuity
- Development of practical computational tools
- Independent verification and validation studies
- Extension of theoretical framework to navigation applications

---

## Repository Contents

### Core Files

**`hammer.ipynb`** - Original Jupyter notebook implementing RVT calculations
- Boost factor computations based on viewing angle (inclination)
- Galaxy rotation curve modeling
- Validation against NGC 891 (edge-on) and M101 (face-on)

**`LICENSE`** - CC0-1.0 Public Domain Dedication (as published by Dr. Karasmanis)

